E(L(G(X), \hat{G}(X))
E(L(G(X), \hat{G}(X)) = E_{X} \sum_{k=1}^{K} L(G_{k}, \hat{G}(X))P(G_{k}|X)
 \hat{G}(x) = \text{argmin}_{g \in G} \sum_{k=1}^{K} L(G_{k},g)P(G_{k}|X=x)
L(G_{k},g) = \begin{cases} 1 \ \ \text{if} \ G_{k} \neq g \\ 0 \ \ \text{if} \ G_{k} = g \end{cases}
